#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/security/_index.adoc:1735
msgid ""
"Before using process accounting, it must be enabled using the following "
"commands:"
msgstr ""
"在使用进程记帐之前， 必须先启用它。 要完成这项工作， 需要运行下面的命令："

